overview: With Superman's death, the country is reeling from the loss. Batman (Ryan Bones) has to get to work to get hopes back up for everyone again. But first, The Flash (Johnny Rapid) stops by to encourage Batman in a way he thinks will not only bring his confidence back up but his big throbbing cock, too. Aquaman (Francois Sagat) is summoned out of the ocean and he immediately hunts for the Green Lantern (Colby Keller) to find out what gay means. The Green Lantern decides it's best to just show him.
